https://forum.sublimetext.com/t/actualvim-perfect-vim-input-for-sublime-text-3/26301

1. Install neovim
    sudo apt-get install neovim
2. Install Actualvim and Configure
    package control
    Preferences -> Package Settings -> ActualVim Settings  
        "neovim_path": "/usr/bin/nvim",
3. Restart
